#Importing dataset
AirPassengers <- read_excel("/Users/shivang/Documents/AirPassengers_1.xlsx")
View(AirPassengers)
AirpassTS <- ts(AirPassengers$Passengers)
plot(AirpassTS)

ndiffs(AirpassTS)
## [1] 1
tsdisplay(AirpassTS)

airtimeseriesdiff1 <- diff(AirpassTS, differences=1)
plot(airtimeseriesdiff1)

tsdisplay(airtimeseriesdiff1)

#Perporming ARIMA
auto_fit <- auto.arima(AirpassTS, trace=TRUE, stepwise = FALSE)

#Residual Analysis
Acf(auto_fit$residuals)

Box.test(residuals(auto_fit), lag=20, type="Ljung")
## 
##  Box-Ljung test
## 
## data:  residuals(auto_fit)
## X-squared = 35.213, df = 20, p-value = 0.019
plot.ts(residuals(auto_fit))

hist(auto_fit$residuals)

tsdiag(auto_fit)

#Forecast for the next five periods
forecast_values <- forecast(auto_fit, h = 5,level=c(99.5))
print(forecast_values)
##    Point Forecast  Lo 99.5  Hi 99.5
## 37       471.6941 346.9828 596.4053
## 38       493.2465 293.7937 692.6994
## 39       497.2933 261.6441 732.9425
## 40       490.6221 243.1509 738.0932
## 41       481.0352 231.0634 731.0069
plot(forecast_values)

#Accuracy of the Model
accuracy <- accuracy(forecast_values)
print(accuracy)
